Author: Luigi21
Title: [ANN]ViMarket - Shop VIRTUALLY, Save In Reality - Disruption of Retail Marketing
Body: The retail marketplace for e-commerce is inefficient. Browsing has shifted from desktop to mobile, worsening the already biggest threat to online retail commerce - Shopping Cart Abandonment - to a now $6.4 Trillion dollar problem. For bigger companies, this means lost revenue, yet for smaller companies, it translates not only into ‘profit loss’ but also an existential threat.  #ViMarket aims to reduce this every year with the help of immersive experiences.  Know more: www.vimarket.io  #RetailShopping #Ecommerce #VRTechnology #VRToken
